'''美人尖'''指[[頭髮|髮]]際（頭髮跟前額的接線）中間向下V字形突出的部分。美人尖有[[遺傳|遺傳]]性，有美人尖為[[顯性基因|顯性基因]]<ref>{{cite book|last=Campbell|first=Neil|authorlink=Neil Campbell (scientist)|coauthors=Jane Reece|title=Biology |url=https://archive.org/details/biology0000camp_07ed|publisher=[[Pearson_Education|Benjamin Cummings]]| date=2005|location=San Francisco|pages=pp. 265}}</ref>。美人尖的英文「widow's peak」（寡婦尖）源自於英國民俗，傳說這個髮型代表女人會活的比其丈夫久<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ask.yahoo.com/20021227.html |title=Where did the term "widow's peak" come from? |access-date=2008-04-14 |archive-date=2012-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312160948/http://ask.yahoo.com/20021227.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[面相|面相]]裡面，常以美人尖作為面相其中一項依據。

